The Philippines 2015 Census of Population (POPCEN 2015)

Source: R/data.R
population_psa_2015.Rd

The Philippines 2015 Census of Population (POPCEN 2015)

population_psa_2015

Format

A tibble with 6 columns and 87567 rows:

area

Area (i.e., country, region, municipality, city) in the Philippines

year

Year (2015 to 2024)

age_category

Five-year age groups

total

Total population

male

Male population

female

Female population

Source

Philippines Statistics Authority
